            <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">Une semaine de douceur de vivre. Des ruelles de la Ponche aux sentiers côtiers de Ramatuelle et vignobles cachés du Var.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-3 border-t border-neutral-100 space-y-2 text-[9px] font-mono">
            <a href="https://booking.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-amber-700 hover:underline font-bold">🏢 Logements de charme</a>
            <a href="https://saily.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-neutral-400 hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">📱 Activer son eSIM France</a>
            <div class="pt-2 text-neutral-900 font-medium uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-neutral-900 w-max pb-0.5 group-hover:text-amber-700 group-hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors cursor-pointer">Découvrir →</div>
