        </div>
        <div class="p-5 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-between space-y-4">
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <span class="text-[8px] font-mono text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest block">Europe // France</span>
            <h2 class="text-base font-serif font-light text-neutral-900 leading-snug group-hover:text-amber-800 transition-colors">Bordeaux & Vignobles</h2>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">7 jours d'immersion culturelle. Splendeurs architecturales de la ville de pierre, Cité du Vin et escapades à Saint-Émilion.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-3 border-t border-neutral-100 space-y-2 text-[9px] font-mono">
            <a href="https://booking.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-amber-700 hover:underline font-bold">🏢 Hôtels Centre Historique</a>
            <a href="https://saily.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-neutral-400 hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">📱 Activer son eSIM Europe</a>
            <div class="pt-2 text-neutral-900 font-medium uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-neutral-900 w-max pb-0.5 group-hover:text-amber-700 group-hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors cursor-pointer">Découvrir →</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- CARD 7 : BASSIN D'ARCACHON -->
      <article class="group flex flex-col justify-between h-full bg-white border border-neutral-200/40 overflow-hidden shadow-2xs hover:shadow-xs transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-full aspect-[16/10] overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 relative">
          <span class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-neutral-950 text-white text-[7px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.1em] px-2 py-0.5 z-10">1 Semaine</span>
          <img src="https://unsplash.com" alt="Guide Arcachon" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-101 transition-transform duration-1000 ease-out" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-between space-y-4">
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <span class="text-[8px] font-mono text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest block">Europe // France</span>
            <h2 class="text-base font-serif font-light text-neutral-900 leading-snug group-hover:text-amber-800 transition-colors">Le Bassin d'Arcachon</h2>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">Une semaine iodée. Ascension de la Dune du Pilat, dégustation d'huîtres dans les cabanes ostréicoles et Cap Ferret.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-3 border-t border-neutral-100 space-y-2 text-[9px] font-mono">
            <a href="https://booking.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-amber-700 hover:underline font-bold">🏢 Réserver ses cabanes</a>
            <a href="https://saily.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-neutral-400 hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">📱 Activer son eSIM France</a>
            <div class="pt-2 text-neutral-900 font-medium uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-neutral-900 w-max pb-0.5 group-hover:text-amber-700 group-hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors cursor-pointer">Découvrir →</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- CARD 8 : BIARRITZ -->
